org.olap4j.metadata

Enum Member.TreeOp

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Member.TreeOp>
      • org.olap4j.metadata.Member.TreeOp
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<Member.TreeOp>, XmlaConstant
    Enclosing interface:
    Member

    public static enum Member.TreeOp
extends Enum<Member.TreeOp>
implements XmlaConstant
    Enumeration of tree operations which can be used when querying members.

    Some of the values are as specified by XMLA. For example, XMLA specifies MDTREEOP_CHILDREN with ordinal 1, which corresponds to the value CHILDREN.

    See Also:
